# Arcstone Science Authority

A public registry of scientific fields, domains, and laws related to permissioned existence and continuity-governed systems.

## Fields
- Authorization Science
- Continuity Science
- Authorization-Centric Substrate Science
- Constitutional Mathematics
- Biological Constitutional Systems

## Structure
- /fields — Field definitions
- /domains — Domain definitions
- /laws — Law statements
- /math — Mathematical primitives
- /kernels — Conceptual kernel cards
- /glossary — Shared vocabulary
- /changelog — Registry updates

All materials are classificatory and theoretical.
